  "detailed_description": "Boom Boomerang is a VR arcade-style boomerang game. Master the skill of throwing and catching virtual boomerangs to destroy bombs before they explode. <br><br>Unlock new boomerangs by collecting awards in Arcade Mode, compete on the global leaderboard in Survival Mode, and fight off the chaos in Onslaught Mode.<br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique gameplay built for VR.<br></li><li>Three game modes: Arcade, Survival and Onslaught.<br></li><li>Global and local leaderboards for each mode and arcade level.<br></li><li>Two difficulty settings with aim-assist available.<br></li><li>Unlockable Boomerangs and Boomerang Trails.<br></li><li>Dynamic environment and music.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202930/extras/6eba670cc359c1a0e71f5a6569cb83cf.poster.avif?t=1672851819\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202930/extras/6eba670cc359c1a0e71f5a6569cb83cf.webm?t=1672851819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202930/extras/6eba670cc359c1a0e71f5a6569cb83cf.mp4?t=1672851819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Boom Boomerang is a VR arcade-style boomerang game. Master the skill of throwing and catching virtual boomerangs to destroy bombs before they explode. <br><br>Unlock new boomerangs by collecting awards in Arcade Mode, compete on the global leaderboard in Survival Mode, and fight off the chaos in Onslaught Mode.<br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique gameplay built for VR.<br></li><li>Three game modes: Arcade, Survival and Onslaught.<br></li><li>Global and local leaderboards for each mode and arcade level.<br></li><li>Two difficulty settings with aim-assist available.<br></li><li>Unlockable Boomerangs and Boomerang Trails.<br></li><li>Dynamic environment and music.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202930/extras/6eba670cc359c1a0e71f5a6569cb83cf.poster.avif?t=1672851819\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202930/extras/6eba670cc359c1a0e71f5a6569cb83cf.webm?t=1672851819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1202930/extras/6eba670cc359c1a0e71f5a6569cb83cf.mp4?t=1672851819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
